name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForPituitaryDisorders
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Pituitary Disorders
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to disorders that result in hyper and/or hypo pituitary function and is listed as a chronic metabolic disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes ACTH deficiency hypopituitarism, hyperpituitarism, hypogonadotropic hypogonadism as well as structural abnormalities such as cysts and nodules.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes acute or transient pituitary gland conditions (such as neonatal or pregnancy related) and pituitary gland neoplasms.)
